title: La Porte New Luxury Community with Resort Style Amenities
posting_body: ['For leasing information call or text', 'show contact info', 'today!!!', 'Ask for ID# 2306A', 'This is the new face of La Porte: an all-inclusive, luxury apartment community in La Porte, Texas where residents engage in every moment and experience life as it should be…in living color.', 'Close out everyday chaos and embrace a new way of living with sleek, modern interiors and designer details…a place where residents can escape beside a resort-inspired pool, challenge themselves inside a 24-hour state-of-the athletic club, or relax with friends at the outdoor beer garden.', 'Create extraordinary moments within this apartment community.', 'Awaken your senses.', 'Resort-inspired pool with sun deck', 'Resident lounge with Billiards, Shuffleboard & Poker Table', 'Beer Garden with yard games and grilling stations', 'Platinum athletic club with cardio theater & Free weights', 'Private dog park with dog wash', 'Free Play Video arcade room', 'Movie screening room', 'Oversized spaces parking available', 'Beautifully landscaped courtyards', 'Convenient to employers, dining, retail, parks, & recreation', 'Clubroom with demonstration kitchen', 'Wi-Fi hot spots', 'Cross training studio', 'Business Lounge with PC and Mac computers', 'Complimentary coffee bar', 'Controlled access parking', 'Private garages and carports available', 'Private yards available', 'On Site Private Car Wash', 'Oversized Garages available']
